phere."}, {"version": "sword", "text": "This Pok\u00e9mon came from another universe. Its gaseous body is so light that even a gentle breeze can blow it away."}, {"version": "ultra-moon", "text": "Whether or not it\u2019s a Pok\u00e9mon from this world is a mystery. When it\u2019s in a jam, it warps away to a safe place to hide."}, {"version": "ultra-sun", "text": "Even though its helpless, gaseous body can be blown away by the slightest breeze, it doesn\u2019t seem to care."}], "entryGameVersions": ["moon", "shield", "sun", "sword", "ultra-moon", "ultra-sun"], "moveGameGroups": ["scarlet-violet", "sun-moon", "sword-shield", "ultra-sun-ultra-moon"], "evolutionRows": [{"stage": 1, "name": "cosmog"}, {"stage": 2, "name": "cosmoem"}, {"stage": 3, "name": "lunala"}, {"stage": 3, "name": "solgaleo"}]}